    • Airport

      public Airport​(java.lang.String name, java.lang.String iata, double longt, double lat)
      Constructs an Airport object with specified name, IATA code, longitude, and latitude. Randomly generates runways and terminals for the airport.
      Parameters:
      name - the name of the airport
      iata - the IATA code of the airport
      longt - the longitude of the airport
      lat - the latitude of the airport

    • getFreeTerminal
